race.description: Share Bets With Tabtouch Bet Loop Hcp (C2)
race.comment: SPARE A PRAYER (1) was quickly into stride over 1200m at this track when resuming last time and dug deep to score well. Drawn to go forward again. Facing a tougher assignment but he is worth serious consideration. KARRI ON (12) has a moderate winning strike-rate but performed well last time at this track, finishing fourth and only 1.75 lengths from the winner at the end of 1100m. Likely improver with strong prospects. CHAMPEZE (9) comes through the same race and progressed nicely last time when finishing just ahead in third. Worth considering but will need some luck from the draw. LIM'S SARBACH (3) never looked likely last time when getting a mile back but did get going late to finish midfield. Will get back again from the draw and be saved for the final shot at them.
